params.markdown:
This dashboard focuses on monitoring directory changes and account activities.

It highlights top users, domains, and Active Directory objects involved in modifications, along with trends in attribute changes and replication events. Password policy checks are tracked by user, workstation, and domain, with detailed logs providing insight into replication syncs and policy enforcement, helping ensure directory integrity and account security.
